    "Name": "Marksman (Light PPC)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Marksman Artillery Vehicle (Light PPC)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>260 Light</color></b>\n\nThe Star League-era Marksman was created as a fire support vehicle to carry the newly designed Sniper Artillery Piece. A successor to the Thor, the Marksman was supposed to use the same chassis, but the weight of the Sniper forced the designers to start with a new design.\n\nArmed with a Sniper artillery piece, this Lyran-built 3068 variant replaces the original Large Laser with a Light Particle Projector Cannon. Four Heavy Machine Guns, two front-mounted and two turret-mounted, enhance its close-range defense. A light fusion engine powers this heavily armed configuration.",
